I am **Sarbajit Mazumdar**, a Ph.D. student in **Theoretical Physics I**
at the **Julius-Maximilians-Universität Würzburg**.

My research lies in theoretical condensed matter physics, with an emphasis on
strongly correlated quantum systems, unconventional superconductivity,
altermagnetism, topology, and quantum transport.
